re Boulez] \u2013 by the Cleveland Orchestra for Boulez's 90th birthday in 2015.\n* [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K04eaqNtVg4 R\u00e9pons in New York] \u2013 short documentary on the October 2017 performances of Boulez's R\u00e9pons at Park Avenue Armory in New York.\n\n'''Interviews'''\n* [https://archive.org/details/SOM_1986_02_16 Charles Amirkhanian interviews Boulez and Andrew Gerzso] as part of the Speaking of Music series, San Francisco, 16 February 1986. Boulez discusses microtonal music, spatial music and ''R\u00e9pons''.\n* [http://www.bruceduffie.com/boulez.html Two Interviews with Pierre Boulez] by Bruce Duffie, 20 February 1986 and 26 October 1987.\n* [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EfIWJ1TIgqQ Filmed interview with Boulez in 2000] with Daniel Barenboim.\n* [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ie5Ore2rjhk Filmed interview with Boulez in 2012] with Wolfgang Schaufler for his publisher, Universal Edition.\n\n'''Images'''\n* [http://www.gontiermusic.com/boulez/index.html Photographic portrait of Pierre Boulez] by Philippe Gontier.\n\n'''Other online resources'''\n* {{Britannica|75540}}\n* [http://www.universaledition.com/composers-and-works/Pierre-Boulez/composer/88/worklist#page=0 Boulez pages at Universal Edition] \u2013 publisher of most of his work, including audio extracts and a calendar of forthcoming performances.\n* [https://www.bbc.co.uk/music/artists/3bce590b-479f-42ca-b9e0-82883e0db9a2 BBC artist page] \u2013 includes interviews with, and about, Boulez and extracts from works.\n* {{AllMusic|class=artist|id=q7088}}\n\n{{Pierre Boulez}}\n{{Twelve-tone technique}}\n{{Twelve-tone composers}}\n{{Darmstadt School}}\n{{BBCSO conductors}}\n{{Cleveland Orchestra conductors}}\n{{Intercontemporain music directors}}\n{{NYPhil music directors}}\n\n{{Navboxes\n|title= Awards for Pierre Boulez\n|list1=\n{{Ernst von Siemens Music Prize}}\n{{Glenn Gould Prize laureates}}\n{{GrawemeyerAwardMusicComposition}}\n{{L\u00e9onie Sonning Music Prize laureates}}\n{{Polar 